&lt;p&gt;Are you digitally-savvy, with an eye for design and excellent attention to detail? Are you passionate about ensuring Sirona’s communications are accessible to all of our audiences?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen in the Communications Team for a Digital and Publications Lead.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post is 30 hours per week (0.8 FTE) for one year and would make an excellent development opportunity for someone looking to strengthen their expertise in digital, branding and accessible communications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please read the attached full job description and if you have further questions please contact Heidi - sirona.recruitment@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
